        <div class="teapot-emoji">ðŸ«–</div>

        <div class="teapot-poem">
            <p><strong>I'm a little teapot,</strong></p>
            <p>Short and stout,</p>
            <p>Here is my handle,</p>
            <p>Here is my spout.</p>
